/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason			
21 Aug 2008	cnwdz2	CCMS Otago 1722 - Thin Client RT Changes: 
                    Assign a function key to btnChangeQueue. 		
*/

